item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Interpol - Zocalo, Mexico (2024)
item.description: Was anyone able to capture the Interpol concert yesterday in the Zocalo of Mexico? I was able to capture the live broadcast via YouTube but it was unstable so the final video is a bit stuck due to the channel that broadcast it on YouTube, is there someone who has captured it in 1080i? It was aired in Mexico so I hope so
item.author: Nero
